Initial: \E Sorry... I don't like this at all.

Original Text: \Eお兄ちゃん…ちょっとしつこい…。
\Eお兄ちゃんが肩を揉んでやろう！

\Eも、もういいよ…。
今度はあたしがお兄ちゃんをマッサージしてあげるね。
Initial:
\E, that's enough...
Next time, I'll give you a massage.
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Tha, that's enough...
Next time, I'll be the one giving you a massage.

Original Text: \E妹に肩を揉んでもらったぞ。

\Eえ、肩を揉んでくれるの？
ありがとうお兄ちゃん。
Initial:
\Eh, you're going to massage my shoulders?
Thank you, oniichan.
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Huh, you're going to give me a shoulders massage?
Thank you, Onii-chan.

Original Text: \Eお兄ちゃんやめ…あはははははくすぐったい！！
Initial: \E Onii-chan, stop... Aha hah! That tickles!!

Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I see... then this will be my payback! Take this!

Original Text: \E妹とくすぐりあいをしたぞ。
\E素でかなり嫌がられてしまった…。
Initial: \She hates me because I'm an E...

Original Text: \E…今はやめておいた方がいいと思うぜ。
Initial: \E... I don't think we should do that right now.
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I shouldn't be doing that right now...

Original Text: \E妹に下着を見せてもらった…。
\Eえ…お兄ちゃんなに言ってるの…。

Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]I ended up embarrassing myself in front her...
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Geez... I suppose there's no helping it...

Original Text: \E…妹のはだかなんか見て面白いの？
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...Is it fun to see your sister's naked body?

Original Text: \Eお兄ちゃん…昔はカッコよかったのにね…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Onii-chan... You used to be so cool back then...

Original Text: \Eお兄ちゃん、それあまりやんない方がいいよ…。
Better translation: \E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Onii-chan, it's better not to do that too much...

Original Text: 深夜パート失敗ルートへ

\E…もうっ！！
…お兄ちゃんの……おにいちゃんの…
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]...I can't take this anymore!!
 ...Onii-chan... you... you...

Original Text:
\E刹那に叩きつけられた衝撃波。
何かの砕ける音、割れる窓、吹き飛ぶ壁。
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]In an instant, a shockwave struck me—a resounding crack of breaking objects, 
the shattering of windows, and the crumbling of walls.

Original Text:
\E横なぎに倒れる木々、吹き飛んだ家…だったもの。
見えるはずのない星空、感じるはずのない夜の風─
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]Trees tumbling sideways, houses blown away—things that were once there. 
An unexpectedly visible starry sky, a night breeze that defies expectation...

Original Text:
\E何が起こったのか？
それらの知覚をついに理解することは叶わなかった。
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]What happened? 
You could never fully grasp the meaning behind those perceptions.

Original Text:
\Eここはただ音もなく、光もなく、何も感じない世界。
即ち無であり永遠であり終着点。
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]This is a world devoid of sound, light, and sensation—a realm of nothingness, 
eternity, and ultimate destination.

Original Text:
\E─ざんねん！
あなたの冒険はここで終わってしまった！
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]What a pity! 
Your adventure has come to an end here!

Original Text:
\E機嫌の悪い時におちんちんびろーんしてはいけません。
容量用法を守ってただしくびろーんしましょう。
Better translation:
\E\font[3]\f[18]\-[2]You shouldn't cause mischief when she's in a bad mood. 
Please treat your sister better; you have failed as an Onii-chan.
